column4: I would like to thank moblet and Fifty for doing a very good server ( good rules, good maps,... )
hope you'll keep the server on in the future, and improving it.
I hope to see you in may 2012 to play with you on the server.
I played on this server with pleasure, online games are surely a great feature :award:

I wish you all a nice game !
